        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8495623-vicki-teague-cooper?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8495623-vicki-teague-cooper?shelf=very-good-story-of-an-incredible-pa">very-good-story-of-an-incredible-pa</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer489800209" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4848676014890652898">I just finished reading this novel--I gotta say it is amazing, glorious, gritty and transformative! This is a book of gritty magical realism--with humor, sadness, quantum physics, samurai, NYC street gangs, metaphysical reveries, war and peace. I recommend it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


